ITEM NO.29               COURT NO.12               SECTION IV-C
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
Petition(s) for Special Leave to Appeal (C)  No(s).  15352/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated  30-01-2025
in WA No. 210/2025 passed by the High Court of Madhya Pradesh at 
Indore]
ZAKI ANWAR ANSARI                                  Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
THE STATE OF MADHYA PRADESH & ORS.                 Respondent(s)
FOR ADMISSION and I.R. 
IA No. 135154/2025 - EXEMPTION FROM FILING O.T.
 
Date : 07-07-2025 This matter was called on for hearing today.
CORAM :  HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE PANKAJ MITHAL
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE K.V. VISWANATHAN
[PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH]
For Petitioner(s)  Mr. Sanjay R Hegde, Sr. Adv.
                   Mr. Anas Tanwir, AOR
                   Mr. Syed Ashhar Ali Warsi, Adv.
                   Mr. Ebad Ur Rahman, Adv.
                   Ms. Zainab Shaikh, Adv.
                   Mr. Fakhre Alam, Adv.
                   Mr. Tanay Hegde, Adv.
                   Ms. Poorvi Asti, Adv.
                   Mr. Hashim Khan, Adv.
                                   
For Respondent(s)  
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
1.Issue notice, returnable within four weeks.
2.Dasti, in addition, is also permitted.
3.In the meantime, parties are directed to maintain status quo,
existing as of today,  with regard to the nature of suit property. 
(VARSHA MENDIRATTA)                             (NIDHI MATHUR)
COURT MASTER (SH)                             COURT MASTER (NSH)
